\f16\b0 \cf0 \uc0\u961 
\f5 \uc0\u8344 \u8336 
\f13 \uc0\u739 
\f16  is a technical parameter that prevents the threat-adaptive rotation formula from producing impossible or degenerate results. It is the maximum path probability value used in the denominator of the rotation formula.\
