\f16\fs24 \cf14 \uc0\u964 
\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f16  = \uc0\u964 
\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f20 \uc0\u8304 
\f16  \'d7 (1 \uc0\u8722  1.0/1.0) = \u964 
\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f20 \uc0\u8304 
\f16  \'d7 0 = 0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 A \uc0\u964 
\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f16  of zero means the honeypot must rotate every zero months \'97 continuously, infinitely. This is physically impossible and operationally meaningless. The formula has collapsed.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f17\b \cf0 \uc0\u961 
\f5\b0 \uc0\u8344 \u8336 
\f6\b \uc0\u739 
\f17  prevents this:
\f16\b0 \
