\f4\b0 \uc0\u8838 
\f17\b  K\'d7K \'97 Pairwise Conflict Set (honeypots that cannot coexist)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f16\b0 \cf0 C is the set of honeypot type pairs that cannot run simultaneously in the same time slot. Each pair (k
\f13 \uc0\u7522 
\f16 , k
\f5 \uc0\u8343 
\f16 ) in C means: if you deploy type k
\f13 \uc0\u7522 
